headline: Here’s Why Baron Real Estate Fund Sold Extra Space Storage (EXR) in Q2
summary: Baron Funds, an investment management company, released its “Baron Real Estate Fund” second-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here.
